{"tid":1672514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我不信任香港的代議制度，但我想大家一齊贏區選","createTime":"2019-10-24T06:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T07:24:16.000Z","uid":324193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a23a7e980a19e81a26a73e5a7a82dbdb83495420","tid":1672514,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:59:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2555660471186224?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2555660471186224%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=eb51982b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2555660471186224?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n香港的選舉制度不完善，問題罄竹難書例如議員被DQ，自由黨周永勤被退選，功能組別引致票值不公等，實際上政府親手DQ了所有無權力的小市民，但我地應該一齊贏區選，因為：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n1. 這是反送中運動短期內的唯一大勝利<br />\n2. 透過助選團進行18區真人流動文宣戰<br />\n3.培育政治人才，備戰立會<br />\n4.和勇合作，和理非再上場的機會<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時化革命<br />\n六大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"cfee34e43960ac769eb14313bb9c9a8c4ab4b47f","tid":1672514,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:04:07.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10<br />\n<br />\n歡迎俾意見，睇下點keep 住港人團火"},{"pid":"4850a83a9fe4c1875920813e0240be8411f58de8","tid":1672514,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"787289aed327227da90cfd4619f9888847f08da8","tid":1672514,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"}]}